---
// src/components/Hero.astro
---

<section class="relative min-h-[85vh] flex flex-col items-center justify-center px-6 overflow-hidden pt-20">
  <!-- Dynamic Background -->
  <div class="absolute inset-0 z-0">
    <div class="absolute top-1/2 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 w-[600px] h-[600px] bg-accent/20 rounded-full blur-[120px]"></div>
    <div class="absolute top-1/4 right-1/4 w-[300px] h-[300px] bg-accent/10 rounded-full blur-[80px]"></div>
  </div>

  <div class="relative z-10 max-w-5xl mx-auto text-center">
    <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl lg:text-8xl font-bold tracking-tight mb-8 leading-[1.1]">
      Превращаем задачи <br />
      <span class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-accent to-accent-glow">
        в прибыль.
      </span>
    </h1>

    <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-gray-400 max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-12 leading-relaxed">
      Создаем IT-решения, которые экономят ресурсы <br class="hidden md:block" /> 
      и масштабируют ваш бизнес.
    </p>

    <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-center gap-4">
      <a 
        href="#contact" 
        class="group relative px-8 py-4 bg-white text-black font-semibold rounded-button overflow-hidden transition-all hover:scale-105 active:scale-95"
      >
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-accent/10 translate-y-full group-hover:translate-y-0 transition-transform duration-300"></div>
        Обсудить проект
      </a>
      <a 
        href="#portfolio" 
        class="px-8 py-4 bg-transparent text-white font-semibold rounded-button border border-white/15 hover:bg-white/5 transition-all hover:scale-105 active:scale-95"
      >
        Смотреть кейсы
      </a>
  </div>
</section>
